sequenceDiagram
    actor Staff
    actor Student
    participant App as Flutter Attendance App
    participant API as Supabase Backend
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Staff->>App: Open event attendance screen
    Student->>App: Present QR / Student ID
    App->>API: Record attendance event
    API->>DB: Insert or update attendance_records
    DB-->>API: Attendance saved

    alt Event linked to requirement
        API->>DB: Create or update requirement_submissions
        DB-->>API: Requirement fulfilled
    end

    API-->>App: Return attendance success
    App-->>Staff: Show recorded status

    Note over API,DB: If event rules or requirement applicability change later
    API->>DB: Revalidate affected clearance items
    DB-->>API: Reset invalid submitted items to on_hold
